analysis: The documents in this cluster primarily concern amendments, extensions, revocations, and modifications of previous executive orders. They cover a wide range of topics including selective service, renegotiation act, atomic energy commission, foreign duty allowances, naval vessels, Panama Canal, District of Columbia alley dwelling act, army and navy air transports, displaced persons commission, Philippine property act, Puerto Rico district court, foreign service act, wage stabilization board, control of the Panama Canal and the Canal Zone, respect for Harry S Truman, German Motor Vessel "CARIBIA", district land office at Carson City, Nevada, Federal Civil Defense Act of 1950, President's Water Resources Policy Commission, Employees' Compensation act, Quetico-Superior Committee, Distinguished Flying Cross, public international organizations, Civil Service Retirement Act and Internal Revenue Code. The sentiment is neutral, as they are legal and administrative directives.
title: Adjustments to Existing Directives
